description: This file serves as the entry point for a React web application. It initializes the app by rendering the main <App /> component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It also imports necessary dependencies and styles.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root from a DOM element for rendering a React application.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders a React component into the root DOM node.
